01:19:12,125 --> 01:19:14,125
[SOJI]
But I'm a boy.

489
01:19:14,958 --> 01:19:17,750
[SOJI] I'm exhausted.
I think I need a nap.

490
01:19:17,833 --> 01:19:19,833
[AIKA] Are you going
to continue on as Tailred?

491
01:19:19,916 --> 01:19:20,916
[SOJI]
Huh?

492
01:19:21,000 --> 01:19:22,125
[AIKA] When we get home,
that secret base

493
01:19:22,208 --> 01:19:23,583
should be finished, right?

494
01:19:23,666 --> 01:19:25,583
You'll need to make a decision.

495
01:19:25,666 --> 01:19:27,875
[SOJI groans]
I've got time.

496
01:19:27,958 --> 01:19:31,291
It's not like they're appearing
in the sky every five minutes.

497
01:19:33,083 --> 01:19:35,125
I wouldn't be so sure.

498
01:19:36,791 --> 01:19:38,541
[DRAGGUILDY] Attention
all peon earthlings

499
01:19:38,625 --> 01:19:40,375
who occupy this planet!

500
01:19:40,458 --> 01:19:42,791
We are the chosen
disciples of the Universe.

501
01:19:42,875 --> 01:19:45,125
We are Ultimaguil!

502
01:19:45,208 --> 01:19:48,375
We have no intention
of bringing you any harm.

503
01:19:48,458 --> 01:19:50,875
All we want is
the powerful light of love

504
01:19:50,958 --> 01:19:52,916
that shines in
each of your hearts.

505
01:19:53,000 --> 01:19:54,791
Resistance is futile!

506
01:19:54,875 --> 01:19:58,000
As long as you do not resist,
your lives will be secure.

507
01:19:58,083 --> 01:19:59,750
Allow us to take
the deep yearnings

508
01:19:59,833 --> 01:20:01,291
of your hearts freely.

509
01:20:01,375 --> 01:20:06,333
Obey! And your days of peace
and tranquility will continue!

510
01:20:08,000 --> 01:20:09,416
[SOJI grunts]

511
01:20:09,500 --> 01:20:11,583
If I let them do this, our
lives won't be secure at all!

512
01:20:11,666 --> 01:20:13,958
If these monsters
take away our desires,

513
01:20:14,041 --> 01:20:15,916
this won't be a world
of peace and tranquility,

514
01:20:16,000 --> 01:20:18,458
it'll be a world full of
apathy and boring hairstyles!

515
01:20:18,541 --> 01:20:21,000
And there's no way in hell
I'm letting that happen!

516
01:20:21,083 --> 01:20:22,458
Does that mean...?

517
01:20:24,666 --> 01:20:26,958
[TWOEARLE] Mr. Soji,
did you see that just now?

518
01:20:27,041 --> 01:20:28,208
Yeah, I sure did.

519
01:20:28,291 --> 01:20:29,583
[TWOEARLE] I'm picking up
Elemelian readings

520
01:20:29,666 --> 01:20:31,541
on the newly finished
base's radar.

521
01:20:31,625 --> 01:20:33,666
