Tell me where?

522
01:20:33,750 --> 01:20:36,041
[TWOEARLE] At Kyuaru High
School, in the next town over.

523
01:20:36,125 --> 01:20:38,958
Okay, I know
exactly where that is.

524
01:20:39,041 --> 01:20:40,541
Here.

525
01:20:40,625 --> 01:20:42,291
[TWOEARLE] I almost forgot, I
thought up an activation code

526
01:20:42,375 --> 01:20:44,291
for Tail Gear, so call it out
when you're ready!

527
01:20:44,375 --> 01:20:46,166
Wait. You mean like
a transformation cry?

528
01:20:46,250 --> 01:20:49,125
[TWOEARLE] Yes. The activation
code is "Tail On"!

529
01:20:49,208 --> 01:20:51,166
[SOJI]
Mm! Mm...

530
01:20:51,250 --> 01:20:53,750
[AIKA]
Mm?

531
01:20:53,833 --> 01:20:55,250
Tail On then!

532
01:21:25,583 --> 01:21:28,375
[TAILRED] I don't understand.
Why Kyuaru High School?

533
01:21:28,458 --> 01:21:29,708
[TWOEARLE]
I can't be certain.

534
01:21:29,791 --> 01:21:31,208
According to the internet,
it's a school that uses

535
01:21:31,291 --> 01:21:34,125
old-style gym uniforms.
Pretty rare these days.

536
01:21:34,208 --> 01:21:36,708
[KYUARU GIRLS screaming]

537
01:21:36,791 --> 01:21:39,708
[TURTLE GUILDY chuckles]

538
01:21:39,791 --> 01:21:41,875
[TURTLE GUILDY] My name
is Turtle Guildy!

539
