546
01:22:04,083 --> 01:22:06,291
[SOJI] By that second day
I had become a celebrity.

547
01:22:06,375 --> 01:22:09,041
Sorry, I mean, Tailred
had become a celebrity.

548
01:22:09,125 --> 01:22:12,458
She was generating a lot of
a buzz all around the world.

549
01:22:12,541 --> 01:22:14,208
Apparently,
even NASA responded to

550
01:22:14,291 --> 01:22:16,708
