declaration of war.

551
01:22:16,791 --> 01:22:19,833
I just hope this thing doesn't
become some kind of a big deal.

552
01:23:53,250 --> 01:23:54,583
[SOJI]
This Tail Gear is awesome!

553
01:23:54,666 --> 01:23:56,500
[TWOEARLE] Yes! The
