557
01:24:01,375 --> 01:24:02,958
[TWOEARLE] Its punching
power is a hundred tons,

558
01:24:03,041 --> 01:24:04,333
and its kicking power
is one fifty!

559
01:24:04,416 --> 01:24:06,208
[AIKA] What about
these Excelion Shorts?

560
01:24:06,291 --> 01:24:07,458
[TWOEARLE] Oh right,
they're shorts that

561
01:24:07,541 --> 01:24:08,666
