and nobody wants to

566
01:24:14,000 --> 01:24:14,791
feel like they're wallowing--

567
01:24:14,875 --> 01:24:15,958
[SOJI]
Okay, that's enough!

568
01:24:16,041 --> 01:24:18,125
Next time: "The Azure
Surge! Tailblue"!

569
01:24:18,208 --> 01:24:19,833
